reviewText: Everything as advertised, he is very good and holds your attention.

He is funny. Clean jokes.  Some I have heard before. I don't think young people would find the jokes funny or possibly know the people he impersonates.  He is a great impersonator which he does often in the act.  I would buy another of his DVD's.
Heard a clip from this at a Women's Conference and wanted to share with a few friends.  It was very entertaining.
Fun, clean entertainment.  We really enjoy and can relate to the humor.  Might order more of his DVD's.  Share it with others also.
I loved seeing Swanberg in person. This is one of his older routines. He's much more entertaining now that he's older.  He spoke at church and used his humour throughout his sermon.
Dennis Swanberg Videos never fail to make me laugh!! I give them away, after I've watched them several times each, just so I can share the fun and laughter he brings to me! I just want to hug him!
Great Christian comedy. We watched it with a group and we were all laughing. It was great for a small group activity.
